  "instructions": [
    "Heat the iron teppan skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the olive oil and swirl it around to coat the bottom of the skillet.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the chopped bell pepper and cook until it is tender.",
    "Add the Irish sausages and cook until they are browned on all sides.",
    "Add the hot chilli powder, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the sausages and vegetables hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
